cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.SY, cs.MA 

The paper proposes a novel reinforcement learning method that uses Gaussian processes to establish cross-member covariances for fleet control. This involves learning to transfer knowledge between similar fleet members and creating member-specific dynamics models for control. Therefore, the paper is likely to belong to the following arXiv CS sub-categories: 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning)
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence)
- cs.RO (Robotics)
- cs.SY (Systems and Control)
- cs.MA (Multi-Agent Systems)
